        .row
          .col-md-6.testimonial
            .face
              img(src="dist/images/testimonials/1453434_391825177587588_1210850387_n.jpg")
            .body
              p.thoughts
                span.quote &ldquo;
                | Kevin and the team at Markev Couriers were the perfect solution to a pressing problem we had at the time. We have been using their services for just over three years now and we do not know what we would do without them. Markev has allowed us to be more efficient by not having to be out and about while providing great rates.

              a(href="http://www.essemmevents.org/", target="_blank").profile &mdash; Essex Events & Communication Inc.

          .col-md-6.testimonial
            .face
